    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "5ff5723a-b240-488a-9f2e-074df0ef8b57",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "5163e1ea-a632-4ce1-806a-eae37cb8f354",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "65dee0b4-427e-4910-95f1-f1bad538e2af",
                            "text": "Look at the Statue",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                                    "imageName": "SamaStatueCU.png"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f80d6807-46fa-4022-9070-721ec0b223d2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The plaque says, \"After years of saving people, fighting evil, and crusading in the name of goodness and honor, Paladinsama made the ultimate sacrifice by giving up his body and soul to restore the Duck of Equilibrium, bringing balance back to the world.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f09e56b0-3a97-4742-90cc-af1276a251b5",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "\"Fortunately, he got better for the sequel. This statue was made three adventures afterwards, while he was training with some monks in the Far East.\" ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4b0c63b4-a5f6-49ba-b597-807192c59114",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I don't know what the Duck of Equilibrium is, or what a \"sequel\" is, but I like the sound of both of them!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "224e5a77-d02a-498d-9f3c-c7e63c7ecb13",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I wonder if all Paladins were named after Paladinsama, or if Paladinsama just decided to live up to his name. Either way, he sounds like one of the biggest of the big-time Heroes!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c6cdfd66-c182-4c7d-9582-e063dc03ca39",
                            "text": "Move the Statue",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a5e9f200-f234-44d2-abf2-4663994acb91",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I'm not that kind of rogue. I'm more of the \"let someone else carry the enormous rock\" kind of rogue.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6097ce26-9558-4f7e-9951-3cbccdb1c95a",
                            "text": "Sense Magic on the Statue",
